snippet.description:
🎒 Planning your dream international vacation? We’ve got the perfect travel partner for you — **Fortune Tours**! ✈️🌍

From visa to flights, hotels to sightseeing, and even special care for kids and senior citizens — Fortune Tours handled our entire **Switzerland trip** with absolute perfection. Every little detail was taken care of, so we could just enjoy the journey and make memories with our family. ❤️

Whether you're a couple, a big family, or a solo traveler, they have **customized packages** that fit your style, comfort, and budget. 💼✨

🌐 Trusted by thousands of happy travellers  
👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 Expert in planning **family trips with kids & seniors**  
🧳 Smooth visa process & 100% support  
📸 Ideal for content creators and vloggers too

Let your next trip be stress-free, scenic, and unforgettable — just like ours!  
#FortuneTours #FamilyTravel #SwitzerlandWithFortune #TravelWithConfidence
🇨🇭 Episode 1 of our Switzerland Vlog Series is HERE!  
Join us — Srinish, Pearle, Nila & Nitara — as we begin our unforgettable journey through one of the most beautiful countries in the world. From airport madness to settling in with the family, this episode is all about love, laughter, and travel chaos! 😄

🎥 In This Episode:

snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

snippet.title: Raavan - Full Movie 4K - Abhishek Bachchan, Vikram, Aishwarya Rai Bachchan, Govinda, Ravi Kishan
snippet.description:
First Time On Youtube - Raavan Full Movie 4K  ab pehli baar YouTube par – woh bhi 4K mein!
Mani Ratnam ki iss epic film mein hai emotion, thrill aur ek aisa jungle jahan sach aur jhooth ka fark mushkil ho jaata hai. Raavan 👹 Full Movie 4K 🔥 Abhishek Bachchan, Vikram, Aishwarya Rai Bachchan, Govinda, Ravi Kishan

एक डाकू एक अधिकारी की पत्नी का अपहरण कर लेता है, उससे प्यार करने लगता है और उसे जाने देता है, लेकिन बाद में उसे एहसास होता है कि वह उससे प्यार करती है। यह एहसास होने पर, उसका अपना पति डाकू तक पहुँचने के लिए उसे बलि का बकरा बनाता है।

निर्देशक - मणिरत्नम
कहानी और पटकथा - मणिरत्नम
संवाद - विजय कृष्ण आचार्य
निर्माता - मणिरत्नम, शारदा त्रिलोक
अभिनीत - अभिषेक बच्चन, विक्रम, ऐश्वर्या राय बच्चन, गोविंदा, निखिल द्विवेदी, रवि किशन, प्रियमणि
छायाकार - संतोष सिवन, वी. मणिकंदन
संपादक - ए. श्रीकर प्रसाद
संगीत - ए. आर. रहमान

#abhishekbachchan #aishwarya #vikram #govinda #ravikishan #priyamani #ravan #mainratnam #bollywoodmovie #firsttimeonyoutube 

A bandit kidnaps an officer's wife, falls in love with her and lets her go, only to realise that she is in love with him. Realising this, her own husband uses her as a scapegoat to reach the bandit.

Director - Mani Ratnam
Story & Screenplay - Mani Ratnam
Dialogues - Vijay Krishna Acharya
Producer - Mani Ratnam, Sharada Trilok
Starring - Abhishek Bachchan, Vikram, Aishwarya Rai Bachchan, Govinda, Nikhil Dwivedi, Ravi Kishan, Priyamani
Cinematographer - Santosh Sivan, V. Manikandan
Editor - A. Sreekar Prasad
Music - A. R. Rahman

snippet.title: Jethalal ने क्यों मारा Iyer की नाक पर लाफ़ा? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Full Movie
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Roshan Singh Sodhi has been absolutely drunk and he is not being allowed back in his house. He tries absolutely crazy things to get back in his house. Will they work? How does excessive consumption of alcohol be a problem for him? Find out in this episode.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 85 - 87
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTXtajBo1G2UEa_wE8BVSU7

snippet.title: Superman | Official Trailer | DC
snippet.description:
Your choices, your actions, that’s what makes you who you are. #Superman - Only In Theaters and @Imax July 11

“Superman,” DC Studios’ first feature film to hit the big screen, is set to soar into theaters worldwide this summer from Warner Bros. Pictures.  In his signature style, James Gunn takes on the original superhero in the newly imagined DC universe with a singular blend of epic action, humor and heart, delivering a Superman who’s driven by compassion and an inherent belief in the goodness of humankind. 

DC Studios heads Peter Safran and Gunn are producing the film, which Gunn directs from his own screenplay, based on characters from DC, Superman created by Jerry Siegel and Joe Shuster.

The film stars David Corenswet (“Twisters,” “Hollywood”) in the dual role of Superman/Clark Kent, Rachel Brosnahan (“The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel”) as Lois Lane and Nicholas Hoult (the “X-Men” movies, “Juror #2”) as Lex Luthor.  The film also stars Edi Gathegi (“For All Mankind”), Anthony Carrigan (“Barry,” “Gotham”), Nathan Fillion (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “The Suicide Squad”), Isabela Merced (“Alien Romulus”), Skyler Gisondo (“Licorice Pizza,” “Booksmart”), Sara Sampaio (“At Midnight”), María Gabriela de Faría (“The Moodys”), Wendell Pierce (“Selma,” “Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan”), Alan Tudyk (“Andor”), Pruitt Taylor Vince (“Bird Box”) and Neva Howell (“Greedy People”).

“Superman” is executive produced by Nikolas Korda, Chantal Nong Vo and Lars Winther.  Behind the camera, Gunn is joined by frequent collaborators, including director of photography Henry Braham, production designer Beth Mickle, costume designer Judianna Makovsky and composer John Murphy, along with composer David Fleming (“The Last of Us”) and editors William Hoy (“The Batman”) and Craig Alpert (“Deadpool 2,” “Blue Beetle”).  

DC Studios Presents a Troll Court Entertainment/The Safran Company Production, A James Gunn Film, “Superman,” which will be in theaters and IMAX® nationwide on July 11, 2025, and internationally beginning 9 July 2025, distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures.

snippet.description:

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Kya Jo Hota Hai Woh Ache Ke Liye Hota Hai? By Sandeep Maheshwari
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

snippet.title: कैरी-मूंग दाल भरवां पराठा-कचौरी वाला स्वाद-नाश्ता या डिनर के लिए परफेक्ट-Raw Mango-Moong dal Paratha
snippet.description:
दाल पराठा तो बहुत खाया होगा अब खाएं कच्चे आम और दाल की भरावन वाला स्पेशल पराठा,  Tangy, Spicy, and So Satisfying – Try This Special Paratha Today,
#paratha #stuffed #breakfast 

Ingredients for 
Kairi - Moong-Dal Stuffed Paratha
For Dough
गेहूँ का आटा - Wheat Flour - 2 cup (300g)
नमक - Salt - ½ tsp
तेल - Oil - 1 tsp
For Stuffing
तेल - Oil - 2 tbsp
कच्चे आम - Raw Mangoes - ¼ cup
पुदीना - Mint Leaves - ½ cup
हरी मिर्च - Green Chilli - 1 no.
अदरक - Ginger - ½  inch
मूंग दाल - Moong Dal - ½ cup
जीरा - Cumin Seeds - ¼ tsp
हींग - Asafoetida - 1 pinch
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric Powder - ¼ tsp
कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri Red Chilli - ½ tsp 
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander Powder - 1 tsp
जीरा पाउडर - Cumin powder - ½ tsp
नमक - Salt - ½ tsp
हरा धनिया - Coriander Leaves

snippet.title: बाप का माल है क्या? जो मुझे चुम्मी देगा 😝 Sridevi - Anil Kapoor Comedy - Roop Ki Rani Choron Ka Raja
snippet.description:
"When a queen rules the world of thieves and a king has explosive plans, you know chaos is bound to follow! Anil Kapoor and Sridevi's electrifying chemistry, Johnny Lever's rib-tickling comedy, and the hilarious antics of Anupam Kher and Paresh Rawal make Roop Ki Rani Choron Ka Raja a laugh riot that will leave you in stitches! Don’t miss this rollercoaster of laughter!"

 "जब चोरों की दुनिया में रानी की धूम मची हो और राजा के इरादों में हो धमाका, तब मस्ती का बवाल तो पक्का है! अनिल कपूर और श्रीदेवी की जबरदस्त जोड़ी, जॉनी लीवर की हंसी से भरपूर कॉमेडी, और अनुपम खेर और परेश रावल के मजेदार अंदाज़ में, Roop Ki Rani Choron Ka Raja आपके पेट में हंसी के गुदगुदी करने वाला सफर है! अगर आप हंसी से लोटपोट होना चाहते हैं, तो ये फिल्म मिस न करें!"

Movie: Roop Ki Rani Choron Ka Raja (1993 )
Cast: Anil Kapoor, Sridevi, Johnny Lever, Jackie Shroff, Anupam Kher, Paresh Rawal
Director: Satish Kaushik
Music Director: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Producer: Boney Kapoor

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: #Video | नईहर के दरजीया | Naihar Ke Darjiya | Pramod Premi Yadav ft. Neelam Giri | New Bhojpuri Song
snippet.description:
नईहर के दरजीया – प्रमोद प्रेमी यादव और नीलम गिरी पर फिल्माया गया एक दिल को छू लेने वाला नया भोजपुरी गीत। इस गीत में नईहर की यादों और भावनाओं को खूबसूरत अंदाज़ में पेश किया गया है। अभी देखें और इस शानदार वीडियो सांग का आनंद लें!

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song Name - Naihar Ke Darjiya 
Hindi - नईहर के दरजीया
Singer - Pramod Premi Yadav 
Music - Arya Sharma
Composer - Chotan Manish
Lyrics - Chotan Manish
Feat - Neelam Giri
Choreographer- Sunny Sonkar
Director- Goldijaiswal 
Dop - Rajan Verma 
Editor - Pappu Verma
Di  - Rohit Singh
Makeup - Jyoti Das
Video by Siddhivinayak Media

Lyrics:-

तोहरा से छोट बड़ होईये नू जाला 
जा ए मरद नाही साइज बुझाला
रोजे रोज के ओरहन आके छोड़ा दी 
नईहर के दरजिया सईया बोला दी 

अंतरा 1 
बुझत नाही बानी हमारा केतना जरूरी बा
देहिया कसाता जैईसे गड़त राजा चूड़ी बा
सीए लागब अपने से हमके सिखा दी 
नईहर के दरजिया सईया बोला दी 

अंतरा 2 
रोजे रोजे आवता डिजाइन नाया नाया 
पेन्हे खातिर प्रमोद हमार तरसता बाया 
छोटन मनीष से कहींके दुख सब हटा दी
नईहर के दरजिया सईया बोला दी

snippet.title: Android 16 FIRST LOOK - Totally Changed !
snippet.description:
naya saal naya maal

🔥 Subscribe for Tabahi Videos

Android 16 is the next major leap in Google’s mobile OS, bringing a wave of AI-powered features, privacy upgrades, and performance improvements to Android smartphones in 2025. With a strong focus on context-aware intelligence, cross-device fluidity, and smoother multitasking, Android 16 is designed to power the next generation of smartphones, tablets, and foldables.

🔍 Top Features of Android 16:

Gemini AI Integration: Smart reply, live summarization, AI-assisted typing, and app-aware suggestions built into the OS.

Lock Screen Widgets 2.0: Deeper customization, glanceable info, and always-on productivity.

Better Background Activity Control: Improved battery life with smarter app hibernation and process management.

Privacy Dashboard 2.0: Real-time app access tracking for microphone, camera, and location usage.

Universal App Streaming: Continue apps seamlessly across Android, ChromeOS, and Windows.

AI-Powered Multilingual Typing: Automatically detects and adapts to the language you’re typing in without switching keyboards.

Revamped Material You Design: Even more dynamic theming, contrast improvements, and adaptive animations.

Improved Foldable & Tablet Support: Enhanced taskbar, split-screen gestures, and large-screen app optimizations.

Android 16 will begin rolling out in beta versions by mid-2025, with the Pixel 9 series and top flagships from Samsung, OnePlus, iQOO, and Vivo among the first to get it.

If you're searching for Android 16 features list, Android 16 eligible devices, or wondering how it compares to iOS 18, this deep dive covers everything you need to know about Google's most intelligent Android version yet.

snippet.title: Justice Bhushan Ramkrishna Gavai takes the oath as the 52nd Chief Justice of India | 14 May 2025
snippet.description:
#chiefjusticeofindia   #supremecourt #cji  #rashtrapatibhavan

Dis: Justice Bhushan Ramkrishna Gavai takes the oath as the 52nd Chief Justice of India, marking a significant chapter in the nation's judicial journey.

President Draupadi Murmu administered the oath of the office of the Chief Justice of India (CJI) to Supreme Court judge Justice  Bhushan Ramkrishna Gavai on Wednesday (14.05.2025)

In a ceremony graced by Vice-President Jagdeep Dhankhar, and Prime Minister Narendra Modi, the new CJI began his tenure with dignity and resolve

snippet.title: Churake - Vilen X Kanika Kapoor (Official Video)
snippet.description:
‘Churake' is a song about a cosmopolitan city girl who falls for a traditional desi guy. As she tries to express her feelings, he consistently pushes her away, burdened by family responsibilities and hesitant to get entangled in a complicated romance. All of this is happening in a delightful, coming-of-age manner.

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
mere samne na ra

Meri saans chadhake na ja na

Ratiyan jagake bhi tu
Mere samne na ra


Na chaal sharabi dekhunga
Na baat nawabi phekunga

Simple saada su chora
Tere haath main aaun na

Tu kyu itraave re chori
Tanne aankh bhi tha ke dekhun na

Manne saaf rehne de
Mann mai mere meil chadhave na

Manne kaam bade se karne
Mere kandhe pe bojh do baatan ka

Sada izzat se karvaani
Kade naak kataani na

Mai jaan nahi mangu

snippet.description:
Gokuldham Society | Gada Electronics | Bonus | Financial Year

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame


Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi

snippet.title: Serious Unemployment Problem | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
We often complain that there are no opportunities to earn a decent living in our state apart from government jobs. But if we look around us, the reality tells a different story. Every day, we see thousands of people from outside the state coming here and earning a good income through various kinds of work, be it small businesses, manual labor, services, or trade. These opportunities are not hidden; they are right in front of our eyes. Yet, we tend to overlook them, thinking they are either beneath us or not worth pursuing.

It is important to understand that it is not the outsiders’ fault for seizing these chances. In fact, they are simply making the most of the opportunities that we ourselves have ignored or failed to recognize. The real issue lies with us, we have become too dependent on limited pathways like government employment, and in doing so, we have allowed others to step in and fill the gap.

The problem is not the lack of opportunity, but our mindset. We need to change the way we look at work and income. We must begin to value dignity in all forms of labor and open our eyes to the many possibilities around us. Instead of complaining, let us take responsibility and start building something for ourselves, in our own land. It's time we rise to the occasion and reclaim the opportunities that are ours to begin with.
This video is just a small satire take on it.

snippet.title: Nobody 2 | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Nobody ruins his vacation. #Nobody2 hits theaters August 15.

---
Sometimes the most dangerous place for a dad is a family vacation.

Bob Odenkirk returns as suburban husband, father and workaholic assassin Hutch
Mansell in the new chapter to Nobody, the hit 2021 bare-knuckle action-thriller that
opened at number one at the U.S. box office.

Four years after he inadvertently took on the Russian mob, Hutch remains $30 million in debt to the criminal organization and is working it off with an unending string of hits on international thugs.

Much as he likes the slam-bang action of his “job,” Hutch and his wife Becca
(International Emmy nominee Connie Nielsen) find themselves overworked and drifting apart. So, they decide to take their kids (Gage Munroe, Paisley Cadorath) on a short getaway to Wild Bill’s Majestic Midway and Waterpark, the one and only place where Hutch and his brother Harry (Grammy and Emmy nominee RZA) went on a vacation as kids.

With Hutch’s dad (Emmy winner Christopher Lloyd) in tow, the family arrives in the small tourist town of Plummerville (“Plummerville is Summerville!”), eager for some fun in the sun.
But when a minor encounter with some town bullies yanks the family into the crosshairs of a corrupt theme-park operator (John Ortiz; Fast and Furious franchise, Bumblebee) and his shady sheriff (Emmy and Golden Globe nominee Colin Hanks), Hutch finds himself the focus of the most unhinged, blood-thirsty crime boss he (or anyone) has ever encountered (Emmy winning and Oscar® nominated screen icon, Sharon Stone).

Nobody 2 is an 87North/Eighty Two Films/Odenkirk Provissiero Entertainment
production, directed by Timo Tjahjanto (The Night Comes for Us, The Big 4). The
screenplay is by returning writer Derek Kolstad (John Wick, Die Hart) and by Aaron
Rabin (Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan), from a story by Derek Kolstad, based on characters created by Derek Kolstad. This film’s returning producers are 87North founders Kelly McCormick (Bullet Train, The Fall Guy) and David Leitch (Bullet Train, The Fall Guy); Odenkirk Provissiero Entertainment founder Marc Provissiero (No Hard Feelings, PEN15), Eighty Two Films founder Braden Aftergood (Hell or High Water, Samaritan); and Bob Odenkirk (Better Call Saul, Breaking Bad). The executive producer is David Hyman.
